WEBVTT

00:00.898 --> 00:03.048
We want New Zealand to be the safest country in the world,...

00:03.926 --> 00:05.205
...but we can't do it without your help.

00:08.905 --> 00:10.600
New Zealand Police are looking for new recruits...

00:10.665 --> 00:11.826
...who can make a real difference,...

00:13.685 --> 00:15.736
...those who care about others and their communities.

00:18.036 --> 00:20.620
We need individuals who want to be a part of a strong team.

00:24.781 --> 00:27.055
When you join the police, you'll be trained with skills to keep you and others safe.

00:28.350 --> 00:33.565
Receive a good starting salary, and you can choose from over 30 different careers...

00:35.226 --> 00:36.342
...like underwater business...

00:37.425 --> 00:38.321
...or youth work...

00:39.089 --> 00:40.391
...or police commissioner stuff.

00:43.984 --> 00:44.323
Drop it.

